comments.body:
Please add tooltips for all columns. You can refer to our web-ui documentation:
https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/d334fee502fa85cfc6ef1b7f193fa3a0ff0b244e/docs/web-ui.md#L416-L447

comments.body: I don't think we need tooltips for every single column.  "IP of the session" does not add anything over the column name. We should only add tooltips where they add something meaningful, like, clarifying for duration fields what the start and end time are exactly.
